          "description": "Read-only endpoints for browsing and fetching individual campaign records."
        },
        {
          "name": "Campaign Management",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "Create Campaign",
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "x-csrf-token",
                    "value": "{{CSRF_TOKEN}}",
                    "description": "CSRF protection token",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "formdata",
                  "formdata": [
                    {
                      "key": "title[en]",
                      "value": "Help Gaza",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "key": "title[ar]",
                      "value": "ساعد غزة",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "key": "description[en]",
                      "value": "Support families in Gaza with essential aid",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "key": "description[ar]",
                      "value": "دعم الأسر في غزة بالمساعدات الأساسية",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "key": "target_amount",
                      "value": "50000",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "key": "current_amount",
                      "value": "0",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "key": "images",
                      "type": "file",
                      "value": null
                    }
                  ]
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/campaign",
                  "host": [
                    "{{BASE_URL}}"
                  ],
                  "path": [
                    "campaign"
                  ]
                },
                "description": "Creates a new donation campaign. Requires an authenticated session with ADMIN or SUPER_ADMIN role.\n\n**Expected User Data**\n`title` (object, multilingual) – Required, e.g. `{ \"en\": \"Help Gaza\", \"ar\": \"ساعد غزة\" }`\n`description` (object, multilingual) – Required, campaign description per supported language\n`target_amount` (number) – Required, fundraising goal (min: 1, max 2 decimal places)\n`current_amount` (number) – Optional, amount already raised (min: 0)\n`images` (file[]) – Optional, one or more image files using field key `images`"
              },
              "response": []
            },
            {
              "name": "Update Campaign",
              "request": {
                "method": "PUT",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "x-csrf-token",
                    "value": "{{CSRF_TOKEN}}",
                    "description": "CSRF protection token",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "formdata",
                  "formdata": [
                    {
                      "key": "title[en]",
                      "value": "Help Gaza – Updated",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "key": "target_amount",
                      "value": "75000",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/campaign/{{CAMPAIGN_ID}}",
                  "host": [
                    "{{BASE_URL}}"
                  ],
                  "path": [
                    "campaign",
                    "{{CAMPAIGN_ID}}"
                  ]
                },
                "description": "Updates an existing campaign. All fields are optional — only provided fields will be updated. Requires ADMIN or SUPER_ADMIN role.\n\n**Expected User Data**\n`id` (string) – Required route parameter, valid UUID of the target campaign\n`title` (object, multilingual) – Optional, updated title per language\n`description` (object, multilingual) – Optional, updated description per language\n`target_amount` (number) – Optional, updated fundraising goal\n`current_amount` (number) – Optional, updated amount raised\n`images` (file[]) – Optional, replacement image files using field key `images`"
              },
              "response": []
            },
            {
              "name": "Delete Campaign",
              "request": {
                "method": "DELETE",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "x-csrf-token",
                    "value": "{{CSRF_TOKEN}}",
                    "description": "CSRF protection token",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/campaign/{{CAMPAIGN_ID}}",
                  "host": [
                    "{{BASE_URL}}"
                  ],
                  "path": [
                    "campaign",
                    "{{CAMPAIGN_ID}}"
                  ]
                },
                "description": "Soft-deletes a campaign by UUID. Requires ADMIN or SUPER_ADMIN role.\n\n**Expected User Data**\n`id` (string) – Required route parameter, valid UUID of the target campaign"
              },
              "response": []
            },
            {
              "name": "Restore Campaign",
              "request": {
                "method": "PATCH",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "x-csrf-token",
                    "value": "{{CSRF_TOKEN}}",
                    "description": "CSRF protection token",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/campaign/restore/{{CAMPAIGN_ID}}",
                  "host": [
                    "{{BASE_URL}}"
                  ],
                  "path": [
                    "campaign",
                    "restore",
                    "{{CAMPAIGN_ID}}"
                  ]
                },
                "description": "Restores a previously soft-deleted campaign back to active state. Requires ADMIN or SUPER_ADMIN role.\n\n**Expected User Data**\n`id` (string) – Required route parameter, valid UUID of the target campaign"
              },
              "response": []
            },
            {
              "name": "Approve Campaign",
              "request": {
                "method": "PATCH",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "x-csrf-token",
                    "value": "{{CSRF_TOKEN}}",
                    "description": "CSRF protection token",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/campaign/approve/{{CAMPAIGN_ID}}",
                  "host": [
                    "{{BASE_URL}}"
                  ],
                  "path": [
                    "campaign",
                    "approve",
                    "{{CAMPAIGN_ID}}"
                  ]
                },
                "description": "Approves a campaign, making it publicly visible. Requires SUPER_ADMIN role only.\n\n**Expected User Data**\n`id` (string) – Required route parameter, valid UUID of the target campaign"
              },
              "response": []
            }
          ],
          "description": "Create, update, delete, restore, and approve campaign records. All endpoints require ADMIN or SUPER_ADMIN authentication."
        }
      ],
      "description": "The Campaign module manages the full lifecycle of donation campaigns — creation, multilingual content, image uploads, status management, and approval workflow."
    },
    {
      "name": "Payment",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Payment Operations",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "Create Payment",
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "x-csrf-token",
                    "value": "{{CSRF_TOKEN}}",
                    "description": "CSRF protection token",
                    "type": "text"
                  },
                  {
                    "key": "idempotency-key",
                    "value": "{{IDEMPOTENCY_KEY}}",
                    "description": "Required. Unique key to ensure idempotent payment creation",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n    \"uuid\": \"{{CAMPAIGN_ID}}\",\n    \"targetType\": \"campaign\",\n    \"amount\": 50,\n    \"provider\": \"IYZICO\"\n}",
                  "options": {
                    "raw": {
                      "language": "json"
                    }
                  }
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/payments/create",
                  "host": [
                    "{{BASE_URL}}"
                  ],
                  "path": [
                    "payments",
                    "create"
                  ]
                },
                "description": "Initiates a donation payment for a campaign. Requires authentication and an idempotency key.\n\n**Expected User Data**\n`uuid` (string) – Required, UUID of the target campaign\n`targetType` (string, enum) – Required, type of donation target. Currently only: `campaign`\n`amount` (number) – Required, donation amount (min: 1)\n`provider` (string, enum) – Required, payment provider. Currently: `IYZICO`\n\n**Headers**\n`idempotency-key` (string) – Required, unique key to prevent duplicate payments"
              },
              "response": []
            },
            {
              "name": "Webhook Handler",
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "stripe-signature",
                    "value": "{{STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SIG}}",
                    "description": "Required for Stripe. Other providers use their own signature headers.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{}",
                  "options": {
                    "raw": {
                      "language": "json"
                    }
                  }
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/payments/webhook/{{PROVIDER}}",
                  "host": [
                    "{{BASE_URL}}"
                  ],
                  "path": [
                    "payments",
                    "webhook",
                    "{{PROVIDER}}"
                  ]
                },
                "description": "Receives and processes payment status updates from a payment provider. This endpoint is called by the provider — NOT by the frontend.\n\n**Expected User Data**\n`provider` (string) – Required route parameter, e.g. `stripe`, `paymob`, `fawry`\nHeaders – Provider-specific signature header (e.g. `stripe-signature` for Stripe)\nBody – Raw payload as sent by the payment provider"
              },
              "response": []
            },
            {
              "name": "Mock Webhook (Dev Only)",
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n    \"type\": \"payment_intent.succeeded\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"object\": {\n            \"id\": \"pi_test_123\",\n            \"metadata\": {\n                \"paymentUuid\": \"{{PAYMENT_ID}}\"\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}",
                  "options": {
                    "raw": {
                      "language": "json"
                    }
                  }
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/payments/mock-webhook/{{PROVIDER}}",
                  "host": [
                    "{{BASE_URL}}"
                  ],
                  "path": [
                    "payments",
                    "mock-webhook",
                    "{{PROVIDER}}"
                  ]
                },
                "description": "Simulates a provider webhook event for local development and testing. Do NOT expose or call this in production.\n\n**Expected User Data**\n`provider` (string) – Required route parameter, e.g. `stripe`, `paymob`, `fawry`\nBody – Any mock payload matching the provider's webhook event format"
              },
              "response": []
            },
            {
              "name": "Get Payment By ID",
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/payments/{{PAYMENT_ID}}",
                  "host": [
                    "{{BASE_URL}}"
                  ],
                  "path": [
                    "payments",
                    "{{PAYMENT_ID}}"
                  ]
                },
                "description": "Retrieves the details and current status of a payment record by its ID.\n\n**Expected User Data**\n`id` (string) – Required route parameter, the payment ID or UUID"
              },
              "response": []
            }
          ],
          "description": "Endpoints for initiating donations, handling provider webhooks, and retrieving payment status records."
        }
      ],
      "description": "The Payment module handles donation payment flows using a pluggable provider architecture. Supports Stripe, Paymob, and Fawry. Includes idempotent webhook processing for real-time payment status updates."
    },
